<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>ðŸ“Š Webhook Performance Report - {{webhookName}}</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366F1 0%, #4F46E5 100%);
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366F1 0%, #4F46E5 50%, #4338CA 100%);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -50%;
      left: -50%;
      width: 200%;
      height: 200%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
      animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg); opacity: 0.7; }
      50% { transform: scale(1.1) rotate(180deg); opacity: 1; }
    }
    .report-icon {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .header-title {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .header-subtitle {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
      font-size: 16px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
      background: white;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .intro-text {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #4a5568;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .webhook-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eef2ff 0%, #e0e7ff 100%);
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 30px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      border-left: 5px solid #6366F1;
    }
    .webhook-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .webhook-icon-small {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366F1 0%, #4F46E5 100%);
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-right: 15px;
    }
    .webhook-title {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #312e81;
    }
    .webhook-details {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    .detail-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 12px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
    }
    .detail-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .detail-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #374151;
      font-size: 14px;
      min-width: 120px;
    }
    .detail-value {
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: right;
      word-break: break-all;
      flex: 1;
    }
    .stats-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .stat-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 25px;
      text-align: center;
      border-left: 4px solid #6366F1;
    }
    .stat-number {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #4F46E5;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .stat-label {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    .success-rate {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #dcfce7 100%);
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 25px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      border-left: 5px solid #10B981;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .success-rate-number {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #059669;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .success-rate-label {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #047857;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .success-rate-description {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #065f46;
      margin-top: 5px;
    }
    .failures-section {
      background: #fef2f2;
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 25px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      border-left: 5px solid #EF4444;
    }
    .failures-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #991b1b;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .failures-icon {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      margin-right: 8px;
    }
    .failure-item {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      border-left: 3px solid #fca5a5;
    }
    .failure-item:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .failure-date {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #991b1b;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .failure-reason {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #dc2626;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .failure-submission {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .no-failures {
      text-align: center;
      color: #10B981;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .performance-insights {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f2937 0%, #111827 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .insights-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #e0e7ff;
    }
    .insights-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .insights-list li {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      padding-left: 20px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .insights-list li::before {
      content: 'ðŸ’¡';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .quick-actions {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 15px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .action-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 15px 25px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .primary-action {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366F1 0%, #4F46E5 100%);
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
    }
    .secondary-action {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
      color: #374151;
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f7fafc;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .footer-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #718096;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .footer-links {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .footer-link {
      color: #6366F1;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 0 15px;
    }
    .footer-link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .email-container { margin: 10px; border-radius: 15px; }
      .header { padding: 30px 20px; }
      .content { padding: 30px 20px; }
      .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .quick-actions { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .detail-row { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
      .detail-value { text-align: left; margin-top: 5px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="report-icon">
        <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white">
          <path d="M3 13h8V3H3v10zm0 8h8v-6H3v6zm10 0h8V11h-8v10zm0-18v6h8V3h-8z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h1 class="header-title">Performance Report</h1>
      <p class="header-subtitle">{{period}} webhook analytics and insights</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h2 class="greeting">Hi {{userName}}! ðŸ‘‹</h2>
      
      <p class="intro-text">
        Here's your {{period}} performance report for webhook "<strong>{{webhookName}}</strong>". 
        This summary shows how your webhook has been performing and highlights any areas that might need attention.
      </p>

      <div class="webhook-card">
        <div class="webhook-header">
          <div class="webhook-icon-small">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white">
              <path d="M3 13h8V3H3v10zm0 8h8v-6H3v6zm10 0h8V11h-8v10zm0-18v6h8V3h-8z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="webhook-title">{{webhookName}}</h3>
        </div>
        
        <div class="webhook-details">
          <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Endpoint URL:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{webhookUrl}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Form:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{formTitle}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Report Period:</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{period}}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="success-rate">
        <span class="success-rate-number">{{successRate}}%</span>
        <div class="success-rate-label">Success Rate</div>
        <div class="success-rate-description">
          {{#if (gt successRate 95)}}
          Excellent! Your webhook is performing very well.
          {{else if (gt successRate 85)}}
          Good performance with room for improvement.
          {{else if (gt successRate 70)}}
          Moderate performance - consider investigating issues.
          {{else}}
          Poor performance - immediate attention recommended.
          {{/if}}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number">{{totalDeliveries}}</span>
          <div class="stat-label">Total Deliveries</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number">{{successfulDeliveries}}</span>
          <div class="stat-label">Successful</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number">{{failedDeliveries}}</span>
          <div class="stat-label">Failed</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number">{{averageResponseTime}}ms</span>
          <div class="stat-label">Avg Response Time</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {{#if recentFailures}}
      {{#if (gt recentFailures.length 0)}}
      <div class="failures-section">
        <h3 class="failures-title">
          <svg class="failures-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#EF4444">
            <path d="M1 21h22L12 2 1 21zm12-3h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2v-4h2v4z"/>
          </svg>
          Recent Failures ({{recentFailures.length}})
        </h3>
        {{#each recentFailures}}
        <div class="failure-item">
          <div class="failure-date">{{date}}</div>
          <div class="failure-reason">{{reason}}</div>
          <div class="failure-submission">Submission: {{submissionId}}</div>
        </div>
        {{/each}}
      </div>
      {{else}}
      <div class="failures-section">
        <div class="no-failures">ðŸŽ‰ No failures during this period!</div>
      </div>
      {{/if}}
      {{/if}}

      <div class="performance-insights">
        <h3 class="insights-title">Performance Insights & Recommendations</h3>
        <ul class="insights-list">
          {{#if (gt successRate 95)}}
          <li>Your webhook is performing excellently with a {{successRate}}% success rate</li>
          <li>Average response time of {{averageResponseTime}}ms is within optimal range</li>
          <li>Continue monitoring for any potential issues</li>
          {{else if (gt successRate 85)}}
          <li>Good performance overall, but there's room for improvement</li>
          <li>Consider investigating the {{failedDeliveries}} failed deliveries</li>
          <li>Monitor response times to ensure they stay optimal</li>
          {{else if (gt successRate 70)}}
          <li>Moderate performance - {{failedDeliveries}} failures need attention</li>
          <li>Check your server logs for common error patterns</li>
          <li>Consider implementing better error handling</li>
          {{else}}
          <li>Poor performance requires immediate attention</li>
          <li>{{failedDeliveries}} failures indicate serious issues</li>
          <li>Review your endpoint configuration and server health</li>
          <li>Consider contacting support for assistance</li>
          {{/if}}
          <li>Set up monitoring alerts for faster issue detection</li>
          <li>Review webhook logs regularly for optimization opportunities</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="quick-actions">
        <a href="{{webhookUrl_manage}}" class="action-button primary-action">
          Manage Webhook
        </a>
        <a href="{{webhookUrl_logs}}" class="action-button secondary-action">
          View Detailed Logs
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p class="footer-text">
        This performance report was generated automatically by {{appName}}. 
        {{#if (lt successRate 85)}}We recommend reviewing your webhook configuration to improve performance.{{else}}Keep up the great work!{{/if}}
      </p>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="footer-link">Dashboard</a>
        <a href="{{webhookUrl_manage}}" class="footer-link">Webhook Settings</a>
        <a href="{{webhookUrl_logs}}" class="footer-link">View Logs</a>
      </div>
      <p class="footer-text" style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #a0aec0;">
        Â© 2025 {{appName}}. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 